es-eu.description: EiTB-ParCC: Parallel Corpus of Comparable News. A Basque-Spanish parallel corpus provided by Vicomtech (https://www.vicomtech.org), extracted from comparable news produced by the Basque public broadcasting group Euskal Irrati Telebista.
es-eu.citation: J. Tiedemann, 2012, Parallel Data, Tools and Interfaces in OPUS. In Proceedings of the 8th International Conference on Language Resources and Evaluation (LREC 2012)
